{"route":{"route":"/posts/7d547224/","outputPath":"posts/7d547224/index.html","kind":"post","title":"gpg使用","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"7d547224"}},"post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/gpg使用.md","route":"/posts/7d547224/","abbrlink":"7d547224","title":"gpg使用","date":"2020-10-02 14:00:01","updated":"2020-10-02 14:00:01","tags":["linux","encrypt"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"生成一个密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --full-gen-key\n```\n\n之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.\n\n创建一个子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --edit-key [key hash]\n\ngpg> addkey\n#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.\n\ngpg> save\n# 保存\n```\n\n导出密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -o /path/gpg_key --export-secret-keys [key hash]\n```\n\n导出子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -o /path/gpg_key.sub --export-secret-subkeys [key hash]\n```\n\n导出吊销证书\n\n```bash\ngpg --generate-revocation [key hash]\n# 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了\n```","excerptHtml":"<p>生成一个密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --full-gen-key</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.</p>\n<p>创建一个子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --edit-key [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg&gt; addkey</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg&gt; save</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 保存</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o /path/gpg_key --export-secret-keys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o /path/gpg_key.sub --export-secret-subkeys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出吊销证书</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --generate-revocation [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了</span></span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"生成一个密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --full-gen-key\n```\n\n之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.\n\n创建一个子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --edit-key [key hash]\n\ngpg> addkey\n#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.\n\ngpg> save\n# 保存\n```\n\n导出密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -o /path/gpg_key --export-secret-keys [key hash]\n```\n\n导出子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -o /path/gpg_key.sub --export-secret-subkeys [key hash]\n```\n\n导出吊销证书\n\n```bash\ngpg --generate-revocation [key hash]\n# 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了\n```\n\n删除密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --delete-secret-keys [key hash]\ngpg --delete-keys [key hash]\n```\n\n导入子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --import /path/gpg_key.sub\n```\n\n查看密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -k\ngpg -K\n```\n\n加密文件\n\n```bash\ngpg -r [user name] -o [output file] -e [filename]\n```\n\n解密\n\n```bash\ngpg -o [output file] -d [filename] # 输出到文件\ngpg -d [filename] # 直接输出到终端\n```\n\n***\n[GPG 加密解密简明教程](https://gist.github.com/jhjguxin/6037564)\n[GPG 的正确使用姿势](https://mogeko.me/2019/068/)","bodyHtml":"<p>生成一个密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --full-gen-key</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.</p>\n<p>创建一个子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --edit-key [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg&gt; addkey</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg&gt; save</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 保存</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o /path/gpg_key --export-secret-keys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o /path/gpg_key.sub --export-secret-subkeys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出吊销证书</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --generate-revocation [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>删除密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --delete-secret-keys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --delete-keys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导入子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --import /path/gpg_key.sub</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>查看密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -k</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -K</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>加密文件</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -r [user name] -o [output file] -e [filename]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>解密</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o [output file] -d [filename] <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 输出到文件</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -d [filename] <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 直接输出到终端</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/jhjguxin/6037564\">GPG 加密解密简明教程</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mogeko.me/2019/068/\">GPG 的正确使用姿势</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"生成一个密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --full-gen-key\n```\n\n之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.\n\n创建一个子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --edit-key [key hash]\n\ngpg> addkey\n#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.\n\ngpg> save\n# 保存\n```\n\n导出密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -o /path/gpg_key --export-secret-keys [key hash]\n```\n\n导出子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -o /path/gpg_key.sub --export-secret-subkeys [key hash]\n```\n\n导出吊销证书\n\n```bash\ngpg --generate-revocation [key hash]\n# 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了\n```\n<!--more-->\n删除密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --delete-secret-keys [key hash]\ngpg --delete-keys [key hash]\n```\n\n导入子密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg --import /path/gpg_key.sub\n```\n\n查看密钥\n\n```bash\ngpg -k\ngpg -K\n```\n\n加密文件\n\n```bash\ngpg -r [user name] -o [output file] -e [filename]\n```\n\n解密\n\n```bash\ngpg -o [output file] -d [filename] # 输出到文件\ngpg -d [filename] # 直接输出到终端\n```\n\n***\n[GPG 加密解密简明教程](https://gist.github.com/jhjguxin/6037564)\n[GPG 的正确使用姿势](https://mogeko.me/2019/068/)\n","plainText":"生成一个密钥 之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了. 创建一个子密钥 导出密钥 导出子密钥 导出吊销证书 删除密钥 导入子密钥 查看密钥 加密文件 解密 GPG 加密解密简明教程 GPG 的正确使用姿势","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"7d547224","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}